## Third-Party Components

This project incorporates or depends upon the following third-party software:

### librtlsdr-2freq
- **License:** GNU General Public License v2.0
- **Author:** DC9ST (Stefan Scholl)
- **Source:** https://github.com/DC9ST/librtlsdr-2freq
- **Description:** Modified librtlsdr for dual-frequency RTL-SDR operation
- **Usage:** Binary execution for data collection

### Go Standard Library
- **License:** BSD-style License
- **Copyright:** The Go Authors
