## Patent Notice

This software implements Time Difference of Arrival (TDOA) techniques for RF 
geolocation. Users should be aware that various patents may exist covering 
TDOA methods and implementations. This software is provided for amateur radio 
experimentation and research purposes. Commercial use may require additional 
patent licensing.

